    dc:description "FIGURE 10A–F. Seira dinizi: head; A, Ant III apical organ; B, clypeal chaetotaxy; C, labral papillae; D, maxillary outer lobe; E, dorsal cephalic chaetotaxy; F, postlabial ventral head, arrow indicates normal ciliated chaetae." ;
